# ğŸ“ University Info-Sharing Platform

A digital platform for MBA students and university stakeholders to access academic and committee-related information with the help of an agentic AI assistant.

---

## ğŸš€ Project Overview

**Goal:** Create a centralized digital platform where students can access course, event, and committee information using natural language queries, powered by AI.

**Duration:** 3 Months (12 Weeks)

**Core Features:**
- Semester calendar view
- Event and course lookup
- Committee and workshop information
- Agentic AI assistant to interpret queries
- Feedback collection and summarization

---

## ğŸ§± Tech Stack

| Layer | Tools |
|------|-------|
| Frontend | React / Streamlit |
| Backend | FastAPI (Python) |
| Database | PostgreSQL |
| AI Assistant | OpenAI GPT-4.5 + LangChain |
| Deployment | Vercel (FE), Render (BE), Railway (DB) |

---

## ğŸ¤– AI Agent Capabilities

- Interpret natural language queries
- Convert into SQL queries (LangChain + OpenAI)
- Query PostgreSQL and fetch data
- Provide formatted results
- Summarize feedback and suggest improvements

## ğŸ“½ï¸ Example User Queries

- "When is the next committee workshop?"
- "Which courses have autonomy?"
- "What did students say about the last CWC event?"
- "List upcoming events hosted by the marketing committee."

